Quick Start
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

./checkoutLLVMClang.sh - Checkout LLVM/Clang
./buildClang.sh release - Build LLVM/Clang
./buildAll.sh release - Build OCLint, and then please find generated
                        binary and libraries at ../build/oclint-release

Detail description can be found at
    http://docs.oclint.org/en/dev/intro/build.html

Compiling in debug mode and enabling testing, please look at
    http://docs.oclint.org/en/dev/devel/compiletest.html
